---
title: Cheesy American Beef Loaded Wedges with Sour Cream
description: A cross between nachos and stuffed baked potatoes, these loaded wedges are the ultimate comfort food. Pile them high with saucy American-spiced beef, Cheddar cheese, charred corn and sour cream, then get cosy and tuck in!
